                "is_heading": 0,
                "text": "The most important \u2018clock' management the consultant body must interact with is the outpatient clinic outcome. The outpatient activity includes the more traditional face to face clinic setting through to results review where patient is not in attendance and is informed of results outcome via a letter. The consequence of incorrect RTT data includes:"
